item.description:
I was talking with @josephruscio on the @heavybit podcast the other day when I realized that vibe coding and agentic engineering have started to blur a bit in some of my work - I published some extracts from the transcript https://t.co/evxoG06Vpa

---
@simonw | ❤️ 3 | 🔁 0 | 💬 0 | 👁 307

I would feel judged for doing donuts in this thing

---
@nickbaumann_ | ❤️ 2 | 🔁 0 | 💬 0 | 👁 187

这两天 AI 用得太猛，把自用的一个 App 搞到几乎不能用…究其原因，除了多线并行+手工验收外，还有一个重要原因是觉得是自用，随意点也没事，结果失控了。幸好还有一个正面例子，那就是给一个上架的 App 修复了一个重要问题。发布产品还是很重要的，即使只有一个用户，都意味着要负责，就不会随意搞。

---
@tualatrix | ❤️ 9 | 🔁 0 | 💬 3 | 👁 679

truly scary: anybody, no matter how noble, can be destroyed by misused AI.

---
@GaryMarcus | ❤️ 14 | 🔁 5 | 💬 2 | 👁 1594
